본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 regenerative medicine (stem cell + tissue engineering + organ regen) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from existing disease entries — regenerative medicine 은 cell therapy + tissue engineering 의 modality 자체. cancer / transplant / pediatric_rare entries 와 modality-substrate overlap 있지만 본 entry 는 **modality-orthogonal**: stem cell mfg + scaffold + small-molecule pharmacology that biases regenerative cell fate. 2024 first FDA MSC therapy = field reset.)

