## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **remestemcel-L Ryoncil 2024** = first FDA MSC therapy after 25+ years of MSC trials. pediatric SR-aGvHD specific. cell-therapy CMC + potency assay challenge 가 historical 의 reason. quantum-VQE scope 의 의미는 small-molecule regen-bias adjuvant (e.g., MSC priming).
2. **BMP-2 Infuse off-label complications** = ectopic bone + cancer signal. dose + scaffold-localization 이 의의. quantum-VQE 의 BMP-receptor selectivity 가 hxq-regen-bmpr-001 candidate motivation (alternative scaffold-localized).
3. **iPSC reprogramming = Yamanaka 2006 → 2024 first iPSC-derived clinical** (Vertex VX-880 T1DM islet). 18-year clinical translation. quantum-VQE 직접 기여 한정 — Yamanaka factor delivery 는 RIBOZYME / VIROCAPSID 가 axis-fit.
4. **senolytic D+Q dasatinib+quercetin** = repurpose, off-label aging trials. selectivity 부족 (dasatinib pan-kinase + quercetin pan-flavonoid). quantum-VQE 의 Bcl-xL selective + reduced thrombocytopenia (navitoclax 의 platelet toxicity) 가 hxq-regen-bclxl-001 motivation.
5. **GDF11 systemic rejuvenation 2014** = Conboy initial → multiple negative replications. mechanism debate. quantum-VQE scope 외부 (assay artifact 의심).
6. **Casgevy + Lyfgenia 2023** = first CRISPR + first AAV gene therapy sickle cell + β-thal. autologous HSC + ex vivo CRISPR + reinfusion. regenerative + transplant + gene-therapy 교차 modality.
7. **Wnt-driven hair follicle / cartilage regen** — small molecule path (CHIR99021 / IIIC3 / VPA) 가 quantum-VQE 의 leverage. cross-link dermatology (alopecia) + msk (cartilage).
8. **3D-bioprinting + decellularized ECM** = WEAVE axis 직접 기여. organ-on-chip vascularization 이 next-frontier.
9. **exosome therapeutics cell-free** = cell-therapy CMC 회피 path. quantum-VQE 의 exosome cargo modeling 한정 (membrane lipid 외 protein).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, regenerative 임상 의미 한정 (cell-therapy 본질이 wet-lab).

